2026-07-05 | v1.0.0 | feat: add architecture-pipeline-durable-state-ac3 skill | Documented crash-safe durable state patterns for pipeline stages: write durable records BEFORE state advance, check idempotency on entry, return FINISH_FAIL on write failures (not RETRY or Continue). AC3 acceptance criteria verified: durable markers exist before state transitions, failures block advance, restart idempotently skips re-applying. Verified on ProjectHephaestus pipeline #1816 (arm_drive_green stage) with 479 unit tests passing.
